data.description: Unbelieveable updates throughout this 2045sq ft home! This 4 bedroom 2.5 bath home has been meticulously readied for the spring market. The whole home has been repainted, new LVP and carpet installed by professionals, new bathroom fixtures, newly stained back deck, new garage door and system and so much more. The spacious yet cozy first floor flows from family room to eat in kitchen to formal dining...great for entertaining or quiet movie nights. Every door has new matte black hardware and all the moldings and baseboards are brand new and professionally installed adding to the crisp look of this home.   The screened in back porch screams sweet tea and warm summer nights and cookouts.  In the kitchen you will find a sweet potential coffee bar area as well as stainless steel appliances, and lots of counter space. Family and friends have plenty of room to gather with you in the kitchen to chat while cooking or let the conversation flow through the great floorplan of this home. Upstairs you will find the lovely primary bedroom with WIC and ensuite bathroom with walk in shower and separate jetted tub. The rest of the upstairs consists of 3 other spacious bedrooms and laundry with washer and dryer that will come with the home.  You will not want to miss the opportunity to see all the updates done to this home.  List of all updates will be available at the home for your convenience. Garage fridge and deep freeze do not convey.
